house.description: A house is a small building that provides shelter for a single family.

small apartment-complex.description: A small apartment-complex is a small building that provides shelter for multiple families.

medium apartment-complex.description: A medium apartment-complex is a medium-sized building that provides shelter for multiple families.

large apartment-complex.description: A large apartment-complex is a large building that provides shelter for multiple families.

extra-large apartment-complex.description: An extra-large apartment-complex is a very large building that provides shelter for multiple families.

market.description: A market is a collection of small shops and stalls that sell a variety of goods and services.

shopping center.description: A shopping center is a large collection of shops and stores that sell a variety of goods and services.

office park.description: An office park is a large collection of offices that provide a variety of services.

industrial park.description: An industrial park is a large collection of factories and warehouses that produce and store goods.

clinic.description: A clinic is a small medical facility or private practice that provides primary care and basic health services.

hospital.description: A hospital is a large medical facility that provides a wide range of health services and medical care.

school.description: A school is a small educational facility that provides basic education and literacy.

university.description: A university is a large educational facility that provides a wide range of educational services and research.
